00:00:06.175 --> 00:00:08.721
Let b represent the number of blue balls

00:00:08.721 --> 00:00:12.109
and let g represent the
number of green balls.

00:00:12.109 --> 00:00:16.234
Let's compare the
expressions 2b and b plus g.

00:00:16.234 --> 00:00:18.079
Which statement is correct?

00:00:18.079 --> 00:00:21.554
So they make a bunch of comparisons
between 2b and b plus g.

00:00:21.554 --> 00:00:23.269
Is it greater than, less than, equal,

00:00:23.269 --> 00:00:25.783
